trans-unit.source: Represents the position of the iterator to the next node in the intersection of two sets of nodes.
trans-unit.target: 두 노드 집합의 교집합에 다음 노드에 대 한 반복기의 위치를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the current result navigator.
trans-unit.target: 현재 결과 탐색기를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The Current property gets modified when the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the Current property to the next node and returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>; otherwise, the Current property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 현재 속성 때 수정 됩니다는 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>메서드를 다음 노드로 현재 속성을 설정 하 고 반환 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>, 그렇지 않으면 현재 속성이 변경 되지 않습니다.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator to the next node in the union.
Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if there are no more nodes.
Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if this function initializes the right nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 반환 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>이 함수에 올바른 중첩 된 반복기를 초기화 하는 경우.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the left-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 반환 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>다음 노드로 왼쪽 중첩 반복기에서 가져와야 하는 경우 필요 합니다.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the next node needs to be fetched from the right-nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: 반환 <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>다음 노드로 오른쪽 중첩 반복기에서 가져와야 하는 경우 필요 합니다.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult>

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult> if the iterator's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.IntersectIterator.Current%2A> property is set to the next node in the iteration.
